Trade/Device Name(s): Diamond Calibrators for Medica ISE Module
Diamond Medica ISE Module Calibrant A
Diamond Medica ISE Module Calibrant B
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Diamond Calibrators for Medica ISE Module, used for calibration of Na+, K+, and Cl- electrodes on PolyChem and Daytona analyzers.
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for in-vitro diagnostics use to provide calibration points for Na+, K+, and Cl- electrodes on PolyChem and Daytona instruments with the Medica ISE Module.
